#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.datasets.make_blobs.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.datasets.make\\_blobs"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_blobs:1 of
msgid "Generate isotropic Gaussian blobs for clustering."
msgstr "生成用于聚类的各向同性高斯斑点。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_blobs:3 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <sample_generators>`."
msgstr "更多信息请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <sample_generators>`。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.datasets.make_blobs.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_blobs:5 of
msgid ""
"If int, it is the total number of points equally divided among clusters. "
"If array-like, each element of the sequence indicates the number of "
"samples per cluster."
msgstr ""
"如果为 int，则表示所有簇中平均分配的点的总数。如果为 array-like，序列中的"
"每个元素表示每个簇的样本数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_blobs:10 of
msgid "The number of features for each sample."
msgstr "每个样本的特征数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_blobs:12 of
msgid ""
"(default=None) The number of centers to generate, or the fixed center "
"locations. If n_samples is an int and centers is None, 3 centers are "
"generated. If n_samples is array-like, centers must be either None or an "
"array of length equal to the length of n_samples."
msgstr ""
"(默认值为 None) 要生成的中心数量，或固定的中心位置。如果 n_samples 是整数"
"且 centers 为 None，则生成 3 个中心。如果 n_samples 是 array-like，则 "
"centers 必须为 None 或者长度等于 n_samples 的数组。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_blobs:18 of
msgid "The standard deviation of the clusters."
msgstr "簇的标准差。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_blobs:20 of
msgid ""
"The bounding box for each cluster center when centers are generated at "
"random."
msgstr "当中心随机生成时，每个簇中心的边界框。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_blobs:23 of
msgid "Shuffle the samples."
msgstr "是否打乱样本顺序。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_blobs:25 of
msgid ""
"Determines random number generation for dataset creation. Pass an int for"
" reproducible output across multiple function calls. See :term:`Glossary "
"<random_state>`."
msgstr ""
"确定数据集创建时的随机数生成方式。传入一个 int 可在多次函数调用中获得可"
"复现的结果。参见 :term:`术语表 <random_state>`。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.datasets.make_blobs.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_blobs:30 of
msgid ""
"* **X** (*tensor of shape [n_samples, n_features]*) -- The generated "
"samples. * **y** (*tensor of shape [n_samples]*) -- The integer labels "
"for cluster membership of each sample."
msgstr ""
"* **X** (*tensor of shape [n_samples, n_features]*) -- 生成的样本。* **y*"
"* (*tensor of shape [n_samples]*) -- 每个样本所属簇的整数标签。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_blobs:30 of
msgid ""
"**X** (*tensor of shape [n_samples, n_features]*) -- The generated "
"samples."
msgstr "**X** (*tensor of shape [n_samples, n_features]*) -- 生成的样本。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_blobs:31 of
msgid ""
"**y** (*tensor of shape [n_samples]*) -- The integer labels for cluster "
"membership of each sample."
msgstr "**y** (*tensor of shape [n_samples]*) -- 每个样本所属簇的整数标签。"

